<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idc4392f7f-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87" identifier="/us/usc/t38/s8510"><num value="8510">§ 8510.</num><heading> Finality of decisions</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Decisions by the Secretary under this subchapter shall not be reviewable administratively by any other officer of the United States.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idc4392f80-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">(<ref href="/us/pl/85/857">Pub. L. 85–857</ref>, <date date="1958-09-02">Sept. 2, 1958</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/72/1259">72 Stat. 1259</ref>, § 5210; renumbered § 8510, <ref href="/us/pl/102/40/tIV/s402/b/1">Pub. L. 102–40, title IV, § 402(b)(1)</ref>, <date date="1991-05-07">May 7, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/238">105 Stat. 238</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/102/83/s4/b/1">Pub. L. 102–83, § 4(b)(1)</ref>, (2)(E), <date date="1991-08-06">Aug. 6, 1991</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/105/404">105 Stat. 404</ref>, 405.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idc4392f81-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idc4392f82-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idc4392f83-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1991—<ref href="/us/pl/102/40">Pub. L. 102–40</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s5210">section 5210 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0"><ref href="/us/pl/102/83">Pub. L. 102–83</ref> substituted “Secretary” for “Administrator”.</p>
</note>
